- Rent a Car - AJS -
- That wonderful feeling – you start the engine and your adventure begins… At Rent a Car - AJS everything we do is about giving you the freedom to discover more. We’ll move mountains to find you the right rental car, and bring you a smooth, hassle-free experience from start to finish.
- We want to make renting a car as simple and personal as driving your own. Renting a car brings you freedom, and we’ll help you find the right car for you at a great price. We use real reviews, genuine customer feedback and our own experience to guide you through your best options. Our customer team is here to support you through your trip, wherever and whenever you need extra help.
- Making sure you have a great experience every time you rent a car makes us happy. We arrange the car rental on your behalf. We use our massive buying power to bring you great deals. You search our app for the car you want. We show you the deals and you can pic any car you want. We confirm your booking for the car. At the end you drive away and you can start your adventure.
- Why use us ? Because we bring you unbeatable value and peace of mind throughout your rental car journey. We use all our experience – and the experiences of millions of our customers – to bring you the car you need and the quality of service you want. Always at the best price.
- Contact us: Email address - racajs@ajs.com Numbers - 011 551 551
